snippet.title: Parasite Eve Trailer psx 8K (Remastered with Neural Network AI)
snippet.description:
I took the original video and used a neural network that is able to Upscale and reconstruct
low-resolution images, keeping most of their elements and details intact. Comparasion 03:34

Enhancements:
Resolution increased from 320x320  to 7680 x4320 pixel.
framerate  increased from 15 fps to 30 fps.
Enhanced lighting effects.
Enhanced Colorization.
Help keep the channel: 
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Upscale
Download  for patreon:
Resolution 7680 x4320 pixels  without youtube compression
#ParasiteEve #psx #ps1 #8k #uspcale
